name: Hiking in Sweet Home

photos.title: Hiking in Sweet Home
photos.description: Todayâs #adventure took us #south again to the @sweethomeoregon area. First stop was #McDowell #Creek County #Park #Majestic #falls and #Royal Terrace falls. Next was the #ghost town of Hwy 20 east of sweet home. Kind of funny and interesting. After that we were off to another set of #hikes. Just across the #bridge and down the road it was Cascadia campgrounds. Soda Falls and Soda Spring Trail. We we got there and a guy said there was some sort of animal on animal attack at the end where the cave was... Well it was not a cave and not an attack. More like someone brushed or sheered their husky. But we did find so extra nice water #views past the end of the trail. A nice dinner stop at #Barsidious Brewing in Lebanon, damn good fryâs and tots.
